{"tid":1722504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚耀宗稱政府不敢「夾硬嚟」堵路擴散料民意逆轉","createTime":"2019-11-15T02:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T02:58:53.000Z","uid":143608,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"89d35388b9a125a7bd6aec664e89e5be3a27ece6","tid":1722504,"uid":143608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:11:08.000Z","msg":"全國人大常委譚耀宗在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，兩間大學的黑衣人分別控制吐露港公路及紅隧，政府不敢「夾硬嚟」，而堵塞的情況不斷擴散，影響市民上班上學，相信民意會逆轉。<br />\n<br />\n他質疑黑衣人的做法，與他們原先所要求的爭取民主自由，是完全相反的方向。<br />\n<br />\n另外，對於警方執法，譚耀宗表示，在衝突現場很多時傳媒的數量較警員多，當拍攝到某些情況，警方都要承擔後果，又以「七警」、「朱經緯」等舉例，指警員都有很大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n被問到警員蒙面難以承擔後果，譚耀宗批評外界將重點顛倒，不斷攻擊警方執法，認為警員不應受太大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492330-20191115.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492330-20191115.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=e215dbda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492330-20191115.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e911be87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492330-20191115.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"bc74582b6b47d165e277a994ec0da0c0b6e0d30e","tid":1722504,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:20:26.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記黃絲入面都大把每日堅持準時返工嘅港豬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd5f6d02de2be59b4fd4681135a6125cc44db8e","tid":1722504,"uid":140326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:24:38.000Z","msg":"而家係藍絲都民意逆轉，覺得你林奠政府太廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022cd280ae6b9911e650f04c48346fa35bf4de28","tid":1722504,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:25:32.000Z","msg":"中共同政府先不嬲最喜歡夾硬黎"},{"pid":"38a03dc684f05792f96bcc07d5deb4036f916a57","ti